snippet.title: RollScape Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2904290/RollScape/
Join on Discord - https://discord.gg/aZ2MamYPKv

Roll, strategize, and upgrade your way to victory in this accessible and ultra-satisfying, yet captivating roguelike. Will you reach the end before running out of rolls?
